  "keyFeatures": [
    "Real-time flight tracking with automatic polling",
    "Interactive Leaflet-based map with multiple base layers",
    "Advanced filtering by airline operator and flight status",
    "Responsive flight detail panels (desktop) and bottom sheets (mobile)",
    "Aircraft photo integration",
    "Smart polling with adaptive intervals based on backend responses"
